 GAM_twist_the_knife_tt:0 " If we somehow beat Texas outright and took all their land, we'll release the Carthaginians as a friend in their lands and let them do their thing while they pay us annual tribute for the privelege of letting them take their homes back. If Texas met its end in some other way, no need to get fancy about it; we'll just throw a big party and hang some captured folks to celebrate. And if any of those other bandit bands are still around? Well, maybe we can invite them over to celebrate too."